 Boys song)|Alive]]\"\n|Best Rap Performance by a Duo or Group\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[47th Annual Grammy Awards|2005]]\n|\"[[Ch-Check It Out]]\"\n|Best Rap Performance by a Duo or Group\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|''To The 5 Boroughs''\n|[[Grammy Award for Best Rap Album|Best Rap Album]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[50th Annual Grammy Awards|2008]]\n|\"Off the Grid\"\n|[[Grammy Award for Best Pop Instrumental Performance|Best Pop Instrumental Performance]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|''The Mix-Up''\n|[[Grammy Award for Best Contemporary Instrumental Album|Best Contemporary Instrumental Album]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[52nd Annual Grammy Awards|2010]]\n|\"[[Too Many Rappers]]\" <small>(featuring [[Nas]])</small>\n|Best Rap Performance by a Duo or Group\n|{{nom}}\n|}\n\n;[[MTV Video Music Award]]s\n{{award table}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[1994 MTV Video Music Awards|1994]]\n|rowspan=\"5\"|\"[[Sabotage (song)|Sabotage]]\"\n|[[MTV Video Music Award for Video of the Year|Video of the Year]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[MTV Video Music Award for Best Group Video|Best Group Video]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[MTV Video Music Award \u2013 Breakthrough Video|Breakthrough Video]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[MTV Video Music Award for Best Direction|Best Direction]] <small>(Director: [[Spike Jonze]])</small>\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[MTV Video Music Award \u2013 Viewer's Choice|Viewer's Choice]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[1998 MTV Video Music Awards|1998]]\n|Beastie Boys\n|[[Michael Jackson Video Vanguard Award]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[1999 MTV Video Music Awards|1999]]\n|\"[[Intergalactic (song)|Intergalactic]]\"\n|[[MTV Video Music Award for Best Hip-Hop Video|Best Hip-Hop Video]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[2009 MTV Video Music Awards|2009]]\n|\"[[Sabotage (song)|Sabotage]]\"\n|Best Video (That Should Have Won a Moonman)\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[2011 MTV Video Music Awards|2011]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|\"[[Make Some Noise (Beastie Boys song)|Make Some Noise]]\"\n|Video of the Year\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Best Direction <small>(Director: [[Adam Yauch]])</small>\n|{{won}}\n|}\n\n;[[MTV Europe Music Awards]]\n{{award table}}\n|-\n|[[1994 MTV Europe Music Awards|1994]]\n|Beastie Boys\n|[[MTV Europe Music Award for Best Group|Best Group]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[1998 MTV Europe Music Awards|1998]]\n|\"[[Intergalactic (song)|Intergalactic]]\"\n|[[MTV Europe Music Award for Best Video|Best Video]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|''Hello Nasty''\n|[[MTV Europe Music Award for Best Album|Best Album]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Beastie Boys\n|Best Group\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[MTV Europe Music Award for Best Hip-Hop|Best Hip-Hop]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[1999 MTV Europe Music Awards|1999]]\n|Beastie Boys\n|Best Hip-Hop\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[2004 MTV Europe Music Awards|2004]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Beastie Boys\n|Best Group\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Best Hip-Hop\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[2011 MTV Europe Music Awards|2011]]\n|\"[[Make Some Noise (Beastie Boys song)|Make Some Noise]]\"\n|Best Video\n|{{nom}}\n|}\n\n;[[MTV Video Music Awards Japan]]\n{{award table}}\n|-\n|[[2005 MTV Video Music Awards Japan|2005]]\n|\"[[Ch-Check It Out]]\"\n|[[MTV Video Music Award Japan for Best Hip-Hop Video|Best Hip-Hop Video]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[2009 MTV Video Music Awards Japan|2009]]\n|Beastie Boys\n|MTV Street Icon Award\n|{{won}}\n|}\n\n==Filmography==\n*''[[Krush Groove]]'' (1985)\n*''[[Tougher Than Leather (film)|Tougher Than Leather]]'' (1988)\n*''[[Futurama]]'' episode \"[[Hell Is Other Robots]]\" (1999)\n*''[[Awesome; I Fuckin' Shot That!]]'' (2006)\n*''[[Fight for Your Right Revisited]]'' (2011)\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n\n{{sisterlinks|wikt=no|mw=no|m=no|species=no|voy=no|v=no|b=no|n=no|s=no|d=Q214039}}\n*{{Books-inline}}\n*{{Official website|http://www.beastieboys.com}}\n* [http://www.beastieboysannotated.com/ Beastie Boys Lyrics Annotated] \u2013 Beastie Boys lyrics laid out with annotated comments explaining popular culture and historical references as well as known samples.\n* [http://www.metrolyrics.com/beastie-boys-lyrics.html Beastie Boys 