|Challenger Series]]''\n===With Frazier===\n\n===With Knierim===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! style=\"background-color: #ffdead; \" colspan=9 align=center | International<ref name=ISU-ASCK/>\n|-\n! Event\n! [[2012\u201313 figure skating season|12\u201313]]\n! [[2013\u201314 figure skating season|13\u201314]]\n! [[2014\u201315 figure skating season|14\u201315]]\n! [[2015\u201316 figure skating season|15\u201316]]\n! [[2016\u201317 figure skating season|16\u201317]]\n! [[2017\u201318 figure skating season|17\u201318]]\n! [[2018\u201319 figure skating season|18\u201319]]\n! [[2019\u201320 figure skating season|19\u201320]]\n|-\n| align=left | [[Figure skating at the Olympic Games|Olympics]] || || || || || || 15th || ||\n|-\n| align=left | [[World Figure Skating Championships|Worlds]] || 9th || || 7th || 9th || 10th || 15th || || WD\n|-\n| align=left | [[Four Continents Figure Skating Championships|Four Continents]] || WD || bgcolor=cc9966 | 3rd || 5th || bgcolor=silver | 2nd || 6th || || || WD\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Grand Prix of Figure Skating Final|Final]] || || || || 7th || || || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Skate America]] || || || 4th || bgcolor=silver | 2nd || || 5th || 4th ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Skate Canada International|Skate Canada]] || || || || || || || || 4th\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Cup of China]] || || 5th || || || WD || || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Internationaux de France|France]] || || || 4th || || || || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Rostelecom Cup]] || || 6th || || || WD || || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[NHK Trophy]] || 4th || || || bgcolor=cc9966 | 3rd || || 5th || bgcolor=cc9966 | 3rd || 7th\n|-\n\n| align=left | {{small|CS}} [[Golden Spin of Zagreb|Golden Spin]] || || || || || || || bgcolor=silver | 2nd ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|CS}} [[Ice Challenge]] || || || || bgcolor=gold | 1st || || || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|CS}} [[Nebelhorn T