om]] |date= December 3, 2015 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=GS160220>{{cite news |title=China's Sui and Han take third Four Continents title|url= https://goldenskate.com/2016/02/4ccs-pairs/|first= Tatjana |last= Flade |work= Golden Skate |date= 20 February 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=IN160628>{{cite news |url= http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2016/06/28/186688092 |title=The Inside Edge: Scimeca, Knierim tie the knot |first= Sarah S. |last= Brannen |work= [[IceNetwork.com]] |date= June 28, 2016 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=USFS160928>{{cite news |url= http://www.usfigureskating.org/story?id=89996&type=media |title= Alexa Scimeca Knierim Medical Update |publisher= [[U.S. Figure Skating]] |date= September 28, 2016 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=USFS170111>{{cite news |url= http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2017/01/11/213294684 |title= Knierims withdraw from 2017 U.S. Championships |publisher= [[IceNetwork.com]] |date= January 11, 2017 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=IN170214>{{cite news |url= http://web.icenetwork.com/news/2017/02/14/215961158/skating-world-braces-for-quad-fest-in-gangneung | title= Skating world braces for quad fest in Gangneung |first= Lynn |last= Rutherford |work= [[IceNetwork.com]] |date= February 14, 2017 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=NBC170321>{{cite news |url= http://olympics.nbcsports.com/2017/03/21/alexa-scimeca-knierim-injury-figure-skating/ | title= Alexa Scimeca Knierim Grateful to Return from Life-threatening Condition |first= Nick |last= Ziccardi |work= [[NBCSports.com]] |date= March 21, 2017 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=FSO170323>{{cite news |url= http://figureskatersonline.com/news/2017/03/23/alexa-scimeca-knierim-and-chris-knierim-return-with-renewed-perspective/ | title= Alexa Scimeca Knierim and Chris Knierim return with renewed perspective |first= Michelle |last= Kennedy |publisher= Figure Skaters Online |date= March 23, 2017 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=RS170403>{{cite news |url= http://www.rockerskating.com/news/2017/4/3/opining-on-2017-worlds-part-3-up-and-down-for-team-usa | title= Opining o