enton]] <br> choreo. by [[Igor Shpilband]] }}\n|\n* [[Hopelessly Devoted to You]]\n* [[You're the One That I Want]]\n* [[Summer Nights (Grease song)|Summer Nights]] <br>{{small| (from [[Grease (film)|Grease]]) }}\n|-\n! 2012\u20132013 <br> <ref name=ISU-1213b/><ref name=ISU-1213a/><ref name=IN130117/>\n|\n* Moonlight Sonata <br>{{small| by [[Ludwig van Beethoven]] }}\n|\n* [[Life Is Beautiful]] <br>{{small| by [[Nicola Piovani]] }}\n----\n* [[The Last of the Mohicans (soundtrack)|Last of the Mohicans]] <br>{{small| by [[Randy Edelman]] }}\n* 500 Nations <br>{{small| by Peter Buffett }}\n|\n* [[Just a Kiss (song)|Just a Kiss]] <br>{{small| by [[Lady Antebellum]] }}\n|}\n\n==Competitive highlights==\n''GP: [[ISU Grand Prix of Figure Skating|Grand Prix]]; CS: [[ISU Challenger Series|Challenger Series]]''\n===With Frazier===\n\n===With Knierim===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! style=\"background-color: #ffdead; \" colspan=9 align=center | International<ref name=ISU-ASCK/>\n|-\n! Event\n! [[2012\u201313 figure skating season|12\u201313]]\n! [[2013\u201314 figure skating season|13\u201314]]\n! [[2014\u201315 figure skating season|14\u201315]]\n! [[2015\u201316 figure skating season|15\u201316]]\n! [[2016\u201317 figure skating season|16\u201317]]\n! [[2017\u201318 figure skating season|17\u201318]]\n! [[2018\u201319 figure skating season|18\u201319]]\n! [[2019\u201320 figure skating season|19\u201320]]\n|-\n| align=left | [[Figure skating at the Olympic Games|Olympics]] || || || || || || 15th || ||\n|-\n| align=left | [[World Figure Skating Championships|Worlds]] || 9th || || 7th || 9th || 10th || 15th || || WD\n|-\n| align=left | [[Four Continents Figure Skating Championships|Four Continents]] || WD || bgcolor=cc9966 | 3rd || 5th || bgcolor=silver | 2nd || 6th || || || WD\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Grand Prix of Figure Skating Final|Final]] || || || || 7th || || || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Skate America]] || || || 4th || b